C:\Data\Nucleus_Dev\Vostok_ACU_A\source\XCategory\Hbl\all\LLIHandler\InputCaptureLLI\InputCaptureLLI.c
      1          /**
      2           *  @file       
      3           *
      4           *  @brief      Basic description of file contents
      5           *
      6           *  @details This module uses 2 methods for capturing the input frequency
      7           *              1. Continuous Conversion Mode -
      8           *                 Conversion is performed continuously. Valid for frequency 2 to 200Hz.
      9           *                 Sampling period is unused in this mode
     10           *
     11           *              2. Discrete Conversion Mode -
     12           *                 Conversion is performed discretely on every sampling period. Valid for frequency above 200Hz. This method avoids overriding of timer interrupt
     13           *                 Sampling period is derived from the setting file which is multiple of 5ms
     14           *
     15           *
     16           *           Filter - Filter is used only if the number of readings are more than 1
     17           *           This method uses the IIR filter for Period and Duty calculation.
     18           *
     19           *
     20           *  Note- 1. Valid Frequency range for the detection is 2Hz to 65KHz
     21           *        2. During testing its observed that the input capture Period readings are accurate for up to 10Khz frequency
     22           *
     23           *  @section    Applicable_Documents
     24           *                  List here all the applicable documents if needed. <tr>
     25           *
     26           *  $Header: InputCaptureLLI.c 1.9 2015/08/10 15:48:11EDT Dasar Hanumanth (DASARHB) Exp  $
     27           *
     28           *  @copyright  Copyright 2015-$Date: 2015/08/10 15:48:11EDT $. Whirlpool Corporation. All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL
     29           */
